# Report

## EXISTING STRUCTURES

None

## ERROR TIPS

### Errors when using extracting but being too far
 -  Make sure to move to the target entity where you want to extract from before extracting items

### Errors when placing into a tile which is occupied by another entity
- Ensure you can place a entity to a tile before attempting placing

### Errors when extracting or inserting items
- Ensure that the source container has items to extract.
- Ensure that the destination container has space to insert items.

### Errors when getting an entity at a specific position
- Ensure that the entity exists at the specified position and is of the correct type. Double-check the coordinates and the entity type.

## NAMESPACE

None
